
current floor > order floor and going down and HallUp 	= (N+1) - d
current floor < order floor and going up and HallDown 	= (N+1) - d


current floor < order floor and going up and HallUp 	= (N+2) - d
current floor > order floor and going down and HallDown = (N+2) - d

current floor > order floor but going up    		= 1
current floor < order floor but going down  		= 1

